compute_inter -- compute the cohesive energy of bulk system
fix_ppm, compute_ppm -- compute the viscosity using periodic perturbation method
fix_imagecharge -- constant constant electrostatic potential simulation with image charge method
fix_chargetransfer -- allow charge to transfer between atoms within a threshold of distance
pair_mie_cut_soft -- soft core version of mie/cut potential for free energy calculation
fix_conp -- constant electrostatic potential simulation with Siepmann & Spirk's method https://github.com/zhenxingwang/lammps-conp